The Metalliferous Mines Regulations 1961<ref>[http://www.novamining.com/knowledgebase/indian-mining-regulations/director-general-of-mines-safety/legislation/the-metalliferous-mines-regulations-1961/], [http://www.dgms.net/mmr.pdf]</ref> replaces both the Metalliferous Mines Regulations-1926 and the Mysore Gold Mines Regulations-1953 to deal with matters for the prevention of possible dangers in mining in India.
